title: “Stats Smackdown”: Iowa — Michigan State

sentences.721c: Here is a comparison of key statistics for the Hawkeyes-Spartans B1G Championship Football Game this Saturday, 12/05/15, at Lucas Oil Stadium in Indianapolis — from HawkeyesMic.com. You can also access the full PDF version here.
